    "id": "v42"
  }, "v42"), mdx("p", null, "T\u1EA5t c\u1EA3 ng\u01B0\u1EDDi Giu-\u0111a tr\u1EA3 l\u1EDDi ng\u01B0\u1EDDi \xCDt-ra-en r\u1EB1ng, \"Ch\xFAng t\xF4i l\xE0m nh\u01B0 th\u1EBF n\u1EA7y v\xEC vua l\xE0 th\xE2n nh\xE2n c\u1EADt ru\u1ED9t c\u1EE7a ch\xFAng t\xF4i. Sao c\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i t\u1EE9c gi\u1EADn l\xE0m g\xEC? Ch\xFAng t\xF4i kh\xF4ng c\xF3 \u0103n nh\u1EDD g\xEC c\u1EE7a vua hay l\u1EA5y v\u1EADt g\xEC ri\xEAng cho ch\xFAng t\xF4i c\u1EA3!\" "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v43"
  }, "v43"), mdx("p", null, "Ng\u01B0\u1EDDi \xCDt-ra-en \u0111\xE1p v\u1EDBi ng\u01B0\u1EDDi Giu-\u0111a, \"Ch\xFAng t\xF4i c\xF3 m\u01B0\u1EDDi chi t\u1ED9c c\u1EE7a \u0110a-v\xEDt, cho n\xEAn ch\xFAng t\xF4i c\xF3 nhi\u1EC1u quy\u1EC1n \u0111\u1ED1i v\u1EDBi \u0110a-v\xEDt h\u01A1n c\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i! Nh\u01B0ng c\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i kh\xF4ng th\xE8m \u0111\u1EBFm x\u1EC9a g\xEC \u0111\u1EBFn ch\xFAng t\xF4i c\u1EA3! Ch\xEDnh ch\xFAng t\xF4i l\xE0 nh\u1EEFng ng\u01B0\u1EDDi \u0111\u1EA7u ti\xEAn b\xE0n \u0111\u1ECBnh vi\u1EC7c mang vua tr\u1EDF v\u1EC1!\" Nh\u01B0ng ng\u01B0\u1EDDi Giu-\u0111a \u0103n n\xF3i gay g\u1EAFt h\u01A1n ng\u01B0\u1EDDi \xCDt-ra-en."), mdx("hr", null), mdx("p", null, "", mdx("a", {
